Package: coauthors
Title: Get list of co-authors from different sources
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hugo",
           family = "Gruson",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "hugo.gruson+R@normalesup.org",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4094-1476"))
Description: Get the list of co-authors for a given person (defined by their 
    name or their ORCiD) from various sources (CrossRef, arXiv, etc.). This can
    be used as a tool to detect conflict of interests when looking for 
    reviewers for a given work.
